citation: Land Use Planning and Approvals (Developments on Mount Wellington) Amendment Act 2013 (Repealed) (Tas)
text:
Land Use Planning and Approvals (Developments on Mount Wellington) Amendment Act 2013 (Repealed)

1. (Repealed)
    The Land Use Planning and Approvals (Developments on Mount Wellington) Amendment Act 2013 has been repealed by Schedule 1 to the Redundant Legislation Repeal Act 2016
